Title: Anyons as quon particles
Authors: V.Bardek, M.Doresic and S.Meljanac
Comments: 10 pages,Latex
Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D49 (1994) 3059-3062
\\
  The momentum operator representation of nonrelativistic anyons is developed
in the Chern - Simons formulation of fractional statistics. The connection
between anyons and the q-deformed bosonic algebra is established.
